The line goes
through these points

00:01:52.420 --> 00:01:53.984
with the equation of a line.

00:01:53.984 --> 00:01:55.400
So the main idea
here is, you only

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:57.360
need 2 points for
an equation of line.

00:01:57.360 --> 00:01:59.110
They've given us
more than necessary.

00:01:59.110 --> 00:02:01.000
